Package: rosepineTheme
Title: Rosé Pine-Inspired Theme for ggplot2
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Jahid", "Hasan", email = "msjahid.ai@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A ggplot2 theme inspired by the Rosé Pine aesthetic with a dark background, vibrant colors, and the Source Code Pro font. Ideal for clean, elegant visualizations.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
